         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">14/10/69 ¶  ¶ Would it be possible, dear Dr Hooker, that I could be obliged with a box ful of roots of Veratrum viride? Perhaps Prof Asa Gray would help in the matter. ¶  This plant in its marvellous ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">69.10.14</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Joseph Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Kew correspondence, Australia, Mueller, 1858-70, f. 408.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation: 'Sent'.</p>
               </note>14/10/69</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Would it be possible, dear Dr Hooker, that I could be obliged with a box ful of roots of <name key="Veratrum%20viride">Veratrum viride</name>? Perhaps Prof Asa Gray would help in the matter.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to J. Hooker, 11 August 1869 (in this edition as 69-08-11b), and M to J. Hooker, 14 August 1869 (in this edition as 69-08-14c).</p>
               </note> This plant in its marvellous effect on the circulation prevents the fibrin-deposits in aneurism &amp; reduces these in an extraordinar manner. I would like therefore to cultivate the plant in Australia. Perhaps <name key="Veratrum%20album">Veratrum album</name> might be had at the same time. Pray do not forget a few roots of Eriophorum polystachy[ar]um.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">E. polystachyum</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(a name not in current use, but in, for example, T. Jones (1875), p. 578), or <seg style="font-style: italic; ">E. polystachion</seg>, M's spelling in B80.04.04, p. 15? See also M to J. Hooker, 14 August 1869 (in this edition as 69-08-14c). The roots requested reached M in January 1870; see M to J. Hooker, 29 January 1870. </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I wonder how my <name key="Todea">Todea</name> arrived.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Always your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eriophorum%20polystachyarum">Eriophorum polystachyarum</name>
            </p>
